==Discography==
{{Main|Lindsay Lohan discography}}
Lohan began showcasing her singing through her acting roles, singing several tracks for the soundtracks of ''Confessions of a Teenage Drama Queen'' and ''Freaky Friday''. Her discography consists of two [[studio album]]s<U+2014>[[Speak (Lindsay Lohan album)|''Speak'']] (2004) and ''[[A Little More Personal (Raw)]]'' (2005)<U+2014>seven [[single (music)|singles]] and five [[music video]]s.

